        "answer": "Yes. The merge flow is designed to preserve WIP, TODO, done, and archive sections."
      },
      {
        "question": "Does it require user approval?",
        "answer": "The migration flow requires confirmation before rewriting AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, or Plans.md."
